{"tid":1426484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"目前和理非行動方案：LOOP一蚊稅、機場集會、遊行","createTime":"2019-08-07T02:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T03:51:35.000Z","uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13cb3f91c7644ff60d161263ff3e3005523db550","tid":1426484,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:30:31.000Z","msg":"關於交一蚊稅：<br />\n因為長期唔交稅佢就會不停加5%同自動係你銀行扣<br />\n咁應付方法就係每次只交一蚊 銀行就要每次倒貼兩蚊<br />\n你俾100佢就要倒貼200<br />\n變相令港共送唔到錢俾支那，唔洗養狗隻打自己<br />\n同時佢又吹你唔漲加唔到5%，何樂而不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於機場集會：<br />\n根據2018年統計，香港機場總流量係7468.8萬人次<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全球排名第8</span><br />\n泰國軍政府之所以跪就係因為人民去搞機場<br />\n你諗下換作香港效果會加大幾多倍<br />\n同埋三罷個日航空業係好成功，而政府特登冷處理<br />\n同時<br />\n搞機場目的係俾外國人知香港情況<br />\n等佢地向外國對香港發出旅遊警告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋香港人好日都唔會入去機場，對咁鐘意返工既港豬根本影響唔到佢地<br />\n<br />\n關於遊行：<br />\n雖然去到目前情況已經包埋TG放題，係呢度我建議和理非帶定豬咀同眼罩<br />\n實行全民勇武，唔洗要你地企前線<br />\n企係後排湊人數已經係一個GOOD SUPPORT<br />\n同埋做禮貌大隊俾中立派轉向我地呢邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且每次遊行完都好多文宣彈俾文宣做野<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7f50dcd70f097737b41e798877db12f406b0e9","tid":1426484,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:38:35.000Z","msg":"十連開始"},{"pid":"dadb7024b13e16265e2043c4fd92760b38be23b0","tid":1426484,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adf367b9e9192a10b07e491fee43c3b141d4082","tid":1426484,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a4ea63aa0527c488ec2f1b023ab28df182e62e","tid":1426484,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704c009f134ec030f8b3f87a8e3b7f3509f60de6","tid":1426484,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2139727d0c1e846e53342c2820d6db532fb43522","tid":1426484,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7084001a3109e53703a0125694d76dcd9306e2","tid":1426484,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c998c4fb467bc514610ee8b759ed7c8091833ae1","tid":1426484,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97037b749532745eddfa647329b6f70df9c0091e","tid":1426484,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a77399db45085d375785ae03ebc12a61778df34","tid":1426484,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:40:22.000Z","msg":"單機連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hk